@kgulaalex:

Are you that blunt? This is not for installation on non-Apple hardware. Trying to install this non-patched, non-osx86 disk image will probably damage your system.

You must be a 'n00b', because everyone knows that setting a new disklabel on a hard drive will fix that problem. What's a disklabel, you ask? Right. n00b.
